externalisedStrings.accountSettings.failedPaymentMessage.com: To successfully set up future payments please check and validate your payment method with the below instructions.

Instructions:
1. To validate the current payment method select the card to be used from the "Delivery Pass" drop down menu via the black arrow and then press the confirm button.
2. To change to another payment method simply click the card to use from the "Delivery Pass" dropdown via the black arrow and press the confirm button.
3. To add a new payment method please click the "Add Payment Type" button and follow the prompts. Please complete the validation check from your bank. When added select the correct card from the drop down menu via the black arrow and click confirm.
externalisedStrings.accountSettings.failedPaymentMessage.non:
To resolve we would kindly ask you to follow the below instructions to update and validate your payment method for current and future payments.
You will need to "Confirm" even if the payment method you wish to use is already in the wallet. Please ensure funds are available.
